      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Why_this_is_the_best_kids_toothbrush_in_uae.png",
        "heading": "Why Choosing the Right Kids Toys and Dental Care Matters",
        "description": "<p>Parents in the UAE are looking for ways to combine fun with functionality. The role of toys has changed, no longer they are the source of entertainment only; instead, they are means of learning, creativity, and development. Along the same lines, dental care products are being improved to make oral hygiene a breeze and a joy for children. Choosing the best mix of toys and dental items can help you:</p><ul><li>Encourage early learning and creativity</li><li>Build healthy dental habits from a young age</li><li>Improve motor skills and cognitive development</li><li>Make daily routines enjoyable instead of stressful<br/></li></ul>",
        "image_position": "left"
      }
    },
    "blocks_xAGhRB": {
