        "ai_gen_block_fa0ee33_LRBnDQ": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_fa0ee33",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Explore the Best Educational Toys in UAE",
            "text": "<p>In the UAE, quality and engagement are important aspects of educational toys in UAE, Quality educational toys stimulate curiosity and improve skills – while keeping kids entertained.by using this principle, I can see what makes this type of toy good at stimulating curiosity and improving children's skills</p><p><br/><strong>2 Year Educational Toys for Early Development</strong></p><p>2 Year Educational Toys for Early DevelopmentAt two years old kids are learning fast. They are getting better at thinking and moving around. Good toys for 2-year-olds help with:<br/>* Finding shape<br/>* Knowing colors<br/>* Solving problems<br/>Using hands and eyes together Some toys are blocks to stack boards, with puzzles and learning kits that let little kids see and learn about the world.</p><p><strong>Creative Learning with Coloring Toys</strong></p><p>Coloring toys are really great for helping kids be creative and express themselves. These toys help kids with a lot of things such as:<br/>* Improving the way they use their hands<br/>* Learning about colors<br/>* Using their imagination<br/>* Focusing and being patient<br/>You can get all sorts of coloring toys like markers that wash off easily and boards that you can draw on again and again. Coloring toys are perfect for kids because they are fun and help them learn at the time. Coloring toys like these are very good, for kids.<br/><strong><br/></strong></p>",
            "desktop_width_percent": 100,
            "text_alignment": "left",
