        "ai_gen_block_7b825c3_MLaWfP": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_7b825c3",
          "settings": {
            "box_1_title": "<h3><br/>Complete Oral Care with Kids Dental Products<br/><br/></h3>",
            "box_1_text": "<p>Oral hygiene is just as important as playtime. Introducing kids to proper dental care early ensures long-term healthy habits.</p><p><strong>Childs Dentist Kit for Fun Learning</strong></p><p>A childs dentist kit makes taking care of teeth fun. These kits usually have:<br/>* Toy dental tools<br/>* Guides to learn about teeth<br/>* Models to practice on<br/>They help kids feel less scared of dentists. They teach kids why brushing teeth. Taking care of teeth is important. They do it in a way. Kids learn about dentist tools. They learn how to take care of their teeth.<br/><strong><br/></strong></p>",
            "box_1_link_text": "Learn more",
            "box_1_link_url": "",
            "box_2_title": "<h3>Kids Electric Toothbrush for Better Cleaning</h3>",
            "box_2_text": "<p>A kids electric toothbrush is a thing that makes brushing teeth a whole lot easier and it really works.<br/>When you compare a kids toothbrush to a regular toothbrush you will see that a kids electric toothbrush has some big advantages, like<br/>* Better plaque removal, which is really important for kids electric toothbrush users<br/><br/>* Gentle brushing action, which is good for kids who use a kids toothbrush<br/><br/>* Fun designs that make kids want to use their kids electric toothbrush.<br/><br/>These kids electric toothbrushes are really helpful, for kids who have a time brushing their teeth the right way with a kids electric toothbrush.<br/></p>",
            "box_2_link_text": "Learn more",
            "box_2_link_url": "",
