          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<p><br/><strong>Advanced Care with Whitening Electric Toothbrush</strong></p><p>An whitening electric toothbrush for older children will help keep their teeth and smile bright, as well as providing a good deep cleaning of their teeth. An electric toothbrush designed for older kids provides:</p><ul><li>Gentle whitening technology</li><li>Safe brushing modes</li><li>Kid-friendly features<br/><br/><br/></li></ul>",
